<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="02 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我說你，<delay8 />對盆栽有興趣嗎？<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可是愛得不能自已喔～！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算說這是我人生旅途中的伴侶，
也絲毫不過分啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說是這麼說啦，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但這條路上學無止境，<delay20 />
我永遠都有學不完的新知咧！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x3 0x4 0x5" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />打個比方<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />你知道<delay8 />
盆栽是利用容器底下的洞<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來固定樹木的嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說是因為<delay8 />如果沒紮實地固定好樹木，<delay20 />
就很難吸收水分跟養分。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是說，無論動物或植物，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />站穩腳跟都很重要啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />打個比方<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />你知道<delay20 />
為什麼在清晨澆水，<delay20 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對盆栽比較好嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說是因為<delay8 />比起在白天澆水，<delay20 />
可以成長得更茁壯的樣子。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的確也喜歡<delay20 />在早上洗澡啊，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟可以帶著清爽的好心情<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開始一天的工作啊！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />打個比方<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />你知道<delay20 />
如果盆栽長大了，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就必須換個容器才行嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說是因為如果在狹窄的空間太久，<delay20 />
就會造成根部腐壞<delay20 />而枯萎喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />的確，<delay20 />我也覺得
比起小房子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大房子住起來更舒適！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="08 00 00 01 00 00 00 09">我問你，<delay8 />你會對自己的東西<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />產生感情嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然聽起來有點像在說教，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是難得剛好聊到這個，你就聽聽吧。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x9 0xa 0xb" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「珍惜物品」這檔子事啊，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可不是拿著就算了喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要「用心、珍惜地使用」，<delay20 />
這才是<delay8 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真正的珍惜物品喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得能夠做到這件事的人，<delay20 />
在跟別人相處的時候，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也才能以一樣的態度尊重對方啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說「對待物品的方式」<delay20 />
最能直接表現出一個人的內心喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當你能珍惜物品，小心使用的話，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />平常的言行舉止<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定也會有著溫柔的氛圍喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你聽過「萬物皆有靈」<delay20 />
這個說法嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果有東西用完不需要了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就兔死狗烹，毫不留情地丟掉，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得實在太冷酷啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真正能幹的人，<delay8 />
就該試著進行加工<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後替它準備好事業的第二春啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="0e 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />無論是誰，
都擁有自己的無價之寶。<delay20 />
你應該也不例外吧？</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0xf 0x10 0x11" /></message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要說我的寶物，<delay20 />
當然不可能是心意卡以外的東西！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />無論是誰送來的，都會讓我很感動，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且卡片上<delay20 />
似乎還傳來了寄件人的心意。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以前收到的卡片，<delay20 />
即使已經破爛不堪了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我就是捨不得丟啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的寶物，<delay20 />
是小時候在河邊撿到的石頭！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />又光亮、又滑順<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在小時候，<delay20 />
甚至相信那是真正的寶石咧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使到現在，也仍然保存在盒子裡，<delay20 />
偶爾還會拿出來鑑賞一番咧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的寶物，<delay20 />是老爸在我小時候<delay8 />
送給我的半壞收音機。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要轉轉刻度盤，<delay20 />就能在雜音中
聽到其他國家的語言跟音樂，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很讓人興奮！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="14 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我真的覺得……<delay frames="40" />
年輕女孩的流行趨勢啊，<delay20 />
實在是很難理解啊……</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x15 0x16 0x17" /></message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我偶爾會看到<delay20 />
有些襯衫或裙子啊，<delay20 />
不是會加上很多蕾絲邊嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種衣服在用熨斗燙的時候，<delay20 />
應該會很麻煩吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />反正<delay20 />我穿的是抗皺襯衫，<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以用不著熨斗就是了！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我偶爾會看到<delay20 />
有種需要綁鞋帶的長靴啊……<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種靴子<delay20 />在穿的時候，<delay8 />
應該既費時又費力吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />換做是我的話，等到鞋子穿完，<delay20 />
大概也累到不想出門了吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我偶爾會看到<delay20 />
有些帽沿特別大的帽子啊……<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種帽子<delay20 />雖然很適合遮陽，<delay20 />
但是真的看得到前面的路嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且只要戴的人靠過來，<delay20 />
好像就會撞到臉上，感覺有點恐怖耶，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025" attrib="1a 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人生只有一次！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就是想要這樣過活！<delay8 />的想法，<delay20 />
有時候會猛烈湧上我的心頭啊。</message>
	<message label="026" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x1b 0x1c 0x1d" /></message>
	<message label="027" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之啦，<delay20 />簡單來說，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是「順從自己的想法過活」啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不說謊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />坦率面對自己的心情！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個說來簡單，<delay20 />
做起來卻很難啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="028" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之啦，<delay20 />簡單來說，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是「努力過活」啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />努力做好現在能做的！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從不後悔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看吧，<delay8 />是不是很帥氣～？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />只要稍微鬆懈，<delay20 />
就會忍不住偷懶了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="029" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之啦，<delay20 />簡單來說，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是「從不半途而廢」啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下定決心後就貫徹到底！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使失敗也不放棄！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看吧，是不是很帥氣～？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過一直受到挫折的話，<delay20 />
也還是免不了會心情沮喪啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>